{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Closing_Act",
  "title": "The Closing Act",
  "summary": "On the final day of the Republic's 20th-Year celebration on New Alderaan, Chief of State Leia Organa-Solo closes a long Senate forum while Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard, the week's Mistress of Events, notes that seven delegates have mysteriously vanished. Hours later, as Leia delivers her closing address in Chianar Plaza, the commemorative holovid is hijacked to replay Palpatine's founding of the Empire, and an explosion tears the roof off the Jedi Temple beneath a projected Imperial starburst. Amid the chaos, security teams evacuate the dignitaries, but Ambrosia's guards prove to be impostors who spirit her, and a horrified, mind-controlled Johanna, away by speeder to the Drosshill scrapyards and aboard a waiting freighter. The Verpine listener Vophsi shepherds its makeshift hive to safety while marine officer Amaya Halos and her Children of Alderaan rally, Han and Chewbacca charge the control kiosk, and the playboy Jaden snaps from boredom to action. The act ends with Ambrosia and Johanna abducted under parasitic control, the attack on the Temple revealed as Johanna's unwilling handiwork.",
